org.junit.jupiter.params.provider

Class ObjectArrayArguments

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.junit.jupiter.params.provider.ObjectArrayArguments
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Arguments

    @API(value=Experimental)
public class ObjectArrayArguments
extends Object
implements Arguments
    Concrete implementation of the Arguments API that provides access to an array of objects to be used for invoking a @ParameterizedTest method.

    A Stream of such Arguments will typically be provided by an ArgumentsProvider.

    Since:
    5.0
    See Also:
    ParameterizedTest, ArgumentsSource, ArgumentsProvider
